      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from sklearn.datasets import make_blobs\n",
        "from sklearn.cluster import KMeans\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import silhouette_score\n",
        "\n",
        "# Mengatur parameter\n",
        "n_samples = 2000\n",
        "n_features = 2\n",
        "centers = 2\n",
        "n_clusters = 5  # Ini adalah jumlah cluster yang diharapkan, meskipun hanya ada dua kategori data\n",
        "random_state = 3 # Mengatur nilai random_state ke 3\n",
        "\n",
        "# Membuat dataset virtual dengan parameter yang telah diatur\n",
        "data, ground_truth = make_blobs(n_samples=n_samples, n_features=n_features, centers=centers, random_state=random_state)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Menampilkan dataset\n",
        "plt.scatter(data[:, 0], data[:, 1], c=ground_truth, cmap='viridis')\n",
        "plt.title(\"Dataset\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Menentukan nilai K optimal\n",
        "silhouette_scores = []\n",
        "for k in range(2, 10):\n",
        "    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=k, random_state=random_state)\n",
        "    kmeans.fit(data)\n",
        "    silhouette_avg = silhouette_score(data, kmeans.labels_)\n",
        "    silhouette_scores.append(silhouette_avg)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Menampilkan grafik elbow untuk pemilihan K optimal\n",
        "plt.plot(range(2, 10), silhouette_scores, marker='o')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('Jumlah Cluster (K)')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('Skor Silhouette')\n",
        "plt.title('Metode Elbow untuk Pemilihan K Optimal')\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Memilih nilai K optimal (misalnya, K=2) dan melakukan clustering\n",
        "best_k = 2\n",
        "kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=best_k, random_state=random_state)\n",
        "kmeans.fit(data)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Menampilkan hasil clustering\n",
        "plt.scatter(data[:, 0], data[:, 1], c=kmeans.labels_, cmap='viridis')\n",
        "plt.scatter(kmeans.cluster_centers_[:, 0], kmeans.cluster_centers_[:, 1], s=200, c='red', label='Centroids')\n",
        "plt.title(f'Hasil Clustering dengan K={best_k}')\n",
        "plt.legend()\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
